data.description: Welcome to 36 Thornberry Lane, located in Devon Green right in the heart of North Stafford! Inside, you'll be greeted by an open layout with vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, and gorgeous natural light creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  This unique layout offers 3 bedrooms upstairs, and a private 4th bedroom mid level with additional space for a small office or sunroom for all of the plant lovers out there! The finished basement offers a large  recreation room and flex space for all of your play dates, movie nights, and get togethers! The 2 tier deck will be the perfect spot for summer gatherings, overlooking the large fenced in yard complete with playground, shed, and fire pit.  The 2-car garage provides ample parking and all the storage space you could want.   Located in a desirable area close to Quantico, shopping centers, and I-95, this home offers convenience and accessibility. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your forever home!
